articles.title: iPhone 16 Pro Teardown Reveals A18 Pro Logic Board Is Smaller, More Densely Packed & Features A Bigger Metal Cover, Likely For Better Heat Transfer - Wccftech
articles.description: The first iPhone 16 Pro teardown has been published on YouTube, revealing a significantly changed A18 Pro logic board compared to the iPhone 15 Pro
articles.content: Apple was previously reported to have introduced a bevy of internal changes that helped address some complaints that iPhone 15 owners were experiencing. Thankfully, the company delivered by radically… [+2019 chars]
